Herman Mashaba has insisted that government lend a hand in putting a stop to the influx of immigrants. The DA mayor met with Malusi Gigaba, Minister of Home Affairs, in discussions about the way forward and to request the minister&#8217;s help in tackling the city&#8217;s immigrant problem. .Last week Mashaba lashed out against foreigners who are in SA, and specifically Johannesburg, illegally; sending a clear warning that his government would track them down.Source eNCA